# Force LF line endings on tracked text files.
# Prevents Windows editors (VS Code/Obsidian) from silently converting files to CRLF,
# which on 2026-05-05 showed up as 96 spurious "M" on .md and 9 more on .py/.sh.
*.md text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
